{"tid":1695807,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"nben自白：我16歲時曾被男人性侵","createTime":"2019-11-06T00:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T04:13:51.000Z","uid":186292,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9ef2e074eb1223bb6057046478602cecfe2589c8","tid":1695807,"uid":186292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T00:39:12.000Z","msg":"人稱「中堅賓」嘅丹麥前阿仙奴前鋒賓特拿，最近喺自傳自爆於2003年新年前夜、16歲時曾被一名男人性侵，事發多年後講番出嚟。<br />\n31歲嘅賓特拿表示，當年自己即將加盟阿仙奴，就喺之前發生性侵事件：「嗰晚真係好誇張，希拉斯(化名)見我同幾個女仔一齊，因此佢好清楚我係直嘅。」<br />\n「我醒來後，發現佢正要玩弄我嘅XX，我嘅反應同任何普通人一樣，我冇打佢，但我好似癲咗咁鬧佢。」賓特拿仲話，佢好快着番衫離開，從此同呢個人絕交。<br />\n賓特拿稱，此人近年試圖聯絡佢，但已經拒絕：「此人活在謊言同虛偽，我唔係呢種人。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20191106/mobile/bkn-20191106041513209-1106_00882_001.html?eventPath=hk_sport&amp;eventID=402881074762b02a0147679f96c4415d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20191106%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191106041513209-1106_00882_001.html%3FeventPath%3Dhk_sport%26eventID%3D402881074762b02a0147679f96c4415d&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGBqcspSF5fyAY0%2FEGx5AO9c%3D&h=5c97f125\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20191106/mobile/bkn-20191106041513209-1106_00882_001.html?eventPath=hk_sport&amp;eventID=402881074762b02a0147679f96c4415d</a>"},{"pid":"e68f9eabeb7a73b78451970de5ce60b3f4a7528e","tid":1695807,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T02:32:58.000Z","msg":"死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3858c2bd741f7c44baac7059d44ec4c7c7d79897","tid":1695807,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T04:13:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />